title: Remove deprecated warnings
body:
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/utils/executor.py:72: The name tf.gfile.Exists is deprecated. Please use tf.io.gfile.exists instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/utils/executor.py:73: The name tf.gfile.MakeDirs is deprecated. Please use tf.io.gfile.makedirs instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/utils/executor.py:127: The name tf.summary.merge is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.summary.merge instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/utils/config.py:224: The name tf.gfile.GFile is deprecated. Please use tf.io.gfile.GFileinstead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/utils/config.py:283: The name tf.gfile.Copy is deprecated. Please use tf.io.gfile.copy instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/networks/base.py:43: The name tf.train.GradientDescentOptimizer is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.train.GradientDescentOptimizer instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/networks/base.py:172: The name tf.summary.histogram is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.summary.histogram instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/networks/classification/base.py:82: The name tf.trainable_variables is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.trainable_variables instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/networks/classification/base.py:102: The name tf.log is deprecated. Please use tf.math.log instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/networks/classification/base.py:107: The name tf.summary.scalar is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.summary.scalar instead. 
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/networks/classification/base.py:130: The name tf.image.resize_images is deprecated. Please use tf.image.resize instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/networks/classification/base.py:182: The name tf.metrics.mean is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.metrics.mean instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/blocks.py:91: The name tf.variable_scope is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.variable_scope instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/lmnet/blocks.py:93: conv2d (from tensorflow.python.layers.convolutional) is deprecated and will be removed in a future version.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/executor/train.py:107: The name tf.placeholder is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.placeholder instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/executor/train.py:125: The name tf.summary.merge_all is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.summary.merge_all instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/executor/train.py:138: The name tf.train.Saver is deprecated. Please use tf.compat.v1.train.Saver instead.
* WARNING:tensorflow:From lmnet/executor/train.py:308: The name tf.train.write_graph is deprecated. Please use tf.io.write_graph instead.
